announcing its financial results for the four month period ended June 30, 2017.
A copy of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report
on Form 8-K.
The information set forth under Item 8.01 below is incorporated into this Item
2.02 by reference.
The information disclosed under Item 2.02, including Exhibit 99.1, is being
furnished and shall not be deemed "filed" for purposes of Section 18 of the
Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended (the "Exchange Act"), or otherwise
subject to the liabilities of that section, and shall not be deemed to be
incorporated by reference in any filing under the Securities Act of 1933, as
amended, or the Exchange Act, except as expressly set forth by specific
reference in such filing.



ITEM 8.01 OTHER EVENTS.



The Company issued a press release on July 27, 2017 titled "RMS Medical Products
Posts Strong Results for Four Month Period Ending June 30, 2017."
