Search for:

















Antibiotic Administration




RMS syringe infusion systems allow antibiotic infusion anywhere, by anyone. These revolutionary systems make IV antibiotic infusion easier than ever for patients and providers.
RMS makes your home infusion experience simpler. The FREEDOM60® and FreedomEdge® are the only pumps designed to employ DynEQ™ (Dynamic Equilibrium) – automatically delivering accurate flow rates, with patient-responsive safety built-in.

Proven patient- and budget-friendly syringe pump systems
More profitability/reduced expenses with reusable pumps
Eliminates hidden complexity and variables of elastomeric devices
Fit almost any dose into 60ml, 30ml, and 20ml syringes
Go Green – environmentally friendly with less medical waste
Antibiotic home infusions are better with the RMS FREEDOM60® and FreedomEdge™


Learn more about RMS antibiotic home infusion solutions – 800-624-9600
 
 




